nodes.text: This building was a large trading establishment located in Cuipernam, capital city of the planet Ansion. In 22 BBY, Jedi Master Luminara Unduli, Jedi Knight Obi-Wan Kenobi, and their Padawans Barriss Offee and Anakin Skywalker sought refuge in the building while under attack by mercenaries hired by Ogomoor, majordomo to Soergg the Hutt.
